1
00:00:29,559 --> 00:00:30,719
I thought

2
00:00:31,640 --> 00:00:32,960
you'd abandoned me.

3
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:46,560
[After arriving in Panyu,]

4
00:00:46,920 --> 00:00:48,439
[we'll switch to land route in Shangzhou.]

5
00:00:48,920 --> 00:00:50,280
[At that time, we can]

6
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:52,759
[ambush and kill the Xiao family's caravan.]

7
00:00:53,640 --> 00:00:54,439
No.

8
00:00:55,439 --> 00:00:56,320
It's not like this.

9
00:00:57,799 --> 00:00:59,240
My father wouldn't do this.

10
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:06,599
You still refuse to admit it?

11
00:01:07,879 --> 00:01:08,640
Yin Xinyue,

12
00:01:10,359 --> 00:01:12,560
I've given you a chance.

13
00:01:13,079 --> 00:01:15,319
Do you dare to say the handwriting and seal on it

14
00:01:15,319 --> 00:01:16,599
are not from him?

15
00:01:16,599 --> 00:01:17,040
Yes.

16
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:18,359
But my father

17
00:01:18,359 --> 00:01:19,959
doesn't know any bandit at all.

18
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:21,599
This...

19
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:23,159
This must be forged.

20
00:01:23,599 --> 00:01:24,599
You have to believe me.

21
00:01:26,959 --> 00:01:28,120
Do you believe

22
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:31,120
I can kill you right now?

23
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:35,519
I'm not lying to you.

24
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,439
For the past six months,

25
00:01:40,359 --> 00:01:42,400
you have repeatedly defended him,

26
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:44,439
and I have repeatedly softened.

27
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:47,400
I'm not lying to you.

28
00:01:49,799 --> 00:01:50,680
Now,

29
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:52,879
and in the past.

30
00:01:54,319 --> 00:01:56,959
I won't believe a single word

31
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:01,280
you say now.

32
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,200
There's one thing

33
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:10,879
you all got wrong.

34
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:13,759
It wasn't my father who sought out Lord Xiao,

35
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:16,080
but Lord Xiao who approached my father.

36
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,840
Since my mother's passing,

37
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,080
my father

38
00:02:23,159 --> 00:02:25,639
hasn't dared to take any risks.

39
00:02:26,479 --> 00:02:27,479
He's terrified

40
00:02:28,479 --> 00:02:30,560
of leaving me alone in this world.

41
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:33,120
He's so afraid of death.

42
00:02:33,759 --> 00:02:35,199
If it weren't for Lord Xiao

43
00:02:35,479 --> 00:02:37,159
hadn't persuaded him with the greater good,

44
00:02:37,719 --> 00:02:40,280
he wouldn't have taken such risks.

45
00:02:41,639 --> 00:02:43,000
Now he's

46
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,199
missing,

47
00:02:45,639 --> 00:02:47,319
his reputation ruined.

48
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,840
All the deeds

49
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:53,599
of Yin Family

50
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:54,439
are here.

51
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,680
They're all here.

52
00:02:56,159 --> 00:02:56,800
Yin,

53
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:58,639
are you sure about this?

54
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:00,759
If it weren't for your persuasion,

55
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,439
a mere merchant like me

56
00:03:02,719 --> 00:03:04,599
shouldn't meddle in such court affairs.

57
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:05,840
But since I've promised you,

58
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,560
I won't back down.

59
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:09,520
Su Erman

60
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,000
knows me inside out.

61
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:13,159
If my mission is exposed,

62
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,039
he will come after me first.

63
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:16,840
At that time,

64
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:18,439
I hope your son

65
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:19,840
will take care of my daughter.

66
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,800
I thought catching Su Erman

67
00:03:24,039 --> 00:03:25,360
would be the end of it.

68
00:03:26,319 --> 00:03:27,240
But it turns out

69
00:03:27,479 --> 00:03:29,439
to be linked to so many

70
00:03:29,599 --> 00:03:31,280
inside dealings of the market.

71
00:03:31,639 --> 00:03:33,800
The forces behind this corruption case

72
00:03:34,039 --> 00:03:35,159
are deeply rooted.

73
00:03:35,919 --> 00:03:36,919
If not cleaned up,

74
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:38,439
this market

75
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:41,960
will become a place for the rich to exploit the poor.

76
00:03:42,879 --> 00:03:43,280
So,

77
00:03:43,759 --> 00:03:46,240
I have to bother you to go with me.

78
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,319
You're welcome.

79
00:03:47,759 --> 00:03:49,080
Although I'm a businessman,

80
00:03:49,599 --> 00:03:50,919
I know the national righteousness.

81
00:03:51,159 --> 00:03:51,840
Don't worry.

82
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,800
I have reported to the Minister.

83
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:54,960
At that time,

84
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,560
the Capital Prefecture will send someone

85
00:03:56,759 --> 00:03:58,439
to the Xiao Family's caravan

86
00:03:58,560 --> 00:03:59,520
to ensure our safety.

87
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:00,439
Perhaps,

88
00:04:00,599 --> 00:04:02,400
the concerns you have today

89
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:03,719
will never come to pass.

90
00:04:03,919 --> 00:04:04,759
At that time,

91
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:05,919
these documents

92
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,599
will be returned to their rightful owner.

93
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:09,919
But Lord Xiao said that day

94
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:13,120
he had never received any letters.

95
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,720
Then why didn't you say so sooner?

96
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:18,560
I didn't say anything because

97
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,720
I didn't want to

98
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:22,040
add more suspicion

99
00:04:22,519 --> 00:04:24,279
to our newly improved relationship.

100
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:25,439
Besides,

101
00:04:25,759 --> 00:04:26,639
seven years ago,

102
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,199
after I broke my promise,

103
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,199
I went to see you,

104
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:31,800
but you refused to meet me.

105
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:33,519
Now you only believe

106
00:04:33,519 --> 00:04:34,720
what you think is the truth.

107
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:37,240
Have you ever really trusted me?

108
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:38,879
If someone tells you

109
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:40,480
your father killed someone

110
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:41,240
and faked his death,

111
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:42,160
would you believe it?

112
00:04:45,199 --> 00:04:46,680
All the evidence now

113
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,360
points to my father.

114
00:04:48,959 --> 00:04:50,079
What can I do

115
00:04:50,279 --> 00:04:51,680
to prove myself?

116
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:55,040
By my loneliness?

117
00:04:55,759 --> 00:04:56,600
Or

118
00:04:57,199 --> 00:04:59,160
our friendship seven years ago?

119
00:05:03,959 --> 00:05:05,199
Thank you, my lord,

120
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,839
for hearing me out.

121
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:11,279
Seven years ago,

122
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:14,639
we each held onto our own truths.

123
00:05:16,199 --> 00:05:17,199
And now,

124
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:20,279
we've hurt each other deeply

125
00:05:23,079 --> 00:05:24,680
over these matters.

126
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:27,759
Today,

127
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:31,360
I only wish to clear my name,

128
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:34,600
to honor my father's memory,

129
00:05:36,439 --> 00:05:38,680
and live up to your father's words

130
00:05:39,160 --> 00:05:40,720
of family and country.

131
00:05:48,959 --> 00:05:50,120
From now on,

132
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:54,240
you and I

133
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,879
go our separate ways,

134
00:05:59,319 --> 00:06:00,480
each finding our own joy.

135
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,199
Very well,

136
00:06:11,759 --> 00:06:12,959
as you wish.

137
00:06:35,199 --> 00:06:36,720
Xinyue was framed.

138
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:38,000
The arsenic incident

139
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,439
is entirely fabricated.

140
00:06:39,639 --> 00:06:41,480
The Capital Prefecture convicted her

141
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,759
and used torture

142
00:06:42,759 --> 00:06:43,959
before the truth was uncovered.

143
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,879
If bias clouds justice,

144
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:47,240
under torture,

145
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,759
anyone can be forced to confess.

146
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,720
If the law loses its fairness,

147
00:06:55,279 --> 00:06:56,800
and power trumps conscience,

148
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:58,560
today it's Madam Yin,

149
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:00,079
tomorrow it could be any of us.

150
00:07:01,279 --> 00:07:02,639
Ms. Lin's words,

151
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:04,360
under torture,

152
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:05,759
anyone would confess.

153
00:07:07,519 --> 00:07:09,480
It truly shocks me.

154
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:12,439
You helped me.

155
00:07:12,639 --> 00:07:14,120
How can I turn a blind eye?

156
00:07:14,879 --> 00:07:16,319
I'm willing to sign the petition

157
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:17,720
to request a retrial.

158
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:20,279
Even if it can't ensure her safety,

159
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:23,319
it will let the world know.

160
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:38,199
May the heavens not forsake us.

161
00:07:38,519 --> 00:07:40,120
and justice is done.

162
00:07:40,519 --> 00:07:42,240
May the good-hearted be rewarded.

163
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:45,920
You'll need to bribe the guards.

164
00:07:46,439 --> 00:07:46,959
This jade bracelet...

165
00:07:50,079 --> 00:07:50,560
This...

166
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:52,199
How can this be?

167
00:07:52,279 --> 00:07:53,040
Without her,

168
00:07:53,279 --> 00:07:55,120
I wouldn't have the courage to face the world.

169
00:07:55,639 --> 00:07:56,360
Take it.

170
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:57,920
Protect her well.

171
00:08:23,839 --> 00:08:25,680
We are all women,

172
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:27,439
born into noble families,

173
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,279
and still have a voice.

174
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:31,680
If we remain silent,

175
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:35,360
where will the women of the world seek justice?

176
00:08:35,879 --> 00:08:36,679
Rest assured,

177
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:39,600
my son works at the Ministry of Justice.

178
00:08:40,679 --> 00:08:41,799
If there is indeed a grievance,

179
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:43,519
he will handle it with fairness.

180
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:47,960
With us here,

181
00:08:49,919 --> 00:08:50,480
don't worry.

182
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,399
Open the door!

183
00:09:04,399 --> 00:09:05,639
Yes, my lord.

184
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:12,879
Minister.

185
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:17,799
Don't move.

186
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:18,799
You're injured.

187
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:19,600
Don't move.

188
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:23,320
I didn't know you were coming.

189
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,039
What brings you here?

190
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:26,480
This is medicine for your wound.

191
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,159
Take it.

192
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:30,039
Take care of yourself.

193
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:32,000
If you need anything else,

194
00:09:32,159 --> 00:09:33,360
just let me know.

195
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:34,679
I'll have my servants prepare it.

196
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,360
Thank you, Lord Xiao.

197
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:39,360
I am unworthy of such

198
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:42,879
consideration from you.

199
00:09:43,519 --> 00:09:45,120
Your father and the Xiao Family

200
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:46,799
have ventured into perilous situations

201
00:09:46,799 --> 00:09:48,080
while assisting me in investigations.

202
00:09:48,679 --> 00:09:50,559
I truly owe you so much.

203
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:52,240
Madam Yin,

204
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,240
don't worry,

205
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,720
everything is for the best.

206
00:09:56,879 --> 00:09:57,679
From now on,

207
00:09:57,919 --> 00:10:00,039
no one in this prison will trouble you.

208
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:02,480
You must take good care of yourself

209
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:04,480
and wait patiently here.

210
00:10:04,879 --> 00:10:05,919
I'll be on my way now.

211
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:21,039
Will Yunzhou blame me?

212
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,679
What do you mean by that?

213
00:10:27,879 --> 00:10:29,240
Your husband's mourning period is almost over.

214
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,480
Regarding the Women's Clinic,

215
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:32,679
I intended to

216
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:35,480
ask Madam Yin to put her career aside

217
00:10:36,039 --> 00:10:37,440
and get married with you.

218
00:10:38,559 --> 00:10:39,559
As a woman,

219
00:10:40,159 --> 00:10:42,480
she should take care of her husband

220
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:43,679
and children.

221
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:46,320
It's not a good idea

222
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,759
to show up in public.

223
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:50,240
But I didn't expect

224
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:53,720
her to hide arsenic in the clinic.

225
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:58,480
You must be overthinking things.

226
00:10:59,039 --> 00:11:00,480
You were just looking out for me.

227
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:02,720
How could I ever blame you?

228
00:11:03,679 --> 00:11:04,799
It's just that Madam Yin

229
00:11:06,159 --> 00:11:07,159
was being careless.

230
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:10,679
Did this cause a fight

231
00:11:10,679 --> 00:11:12,440
between you and Madam Yin?

232
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:16,480
Then I would truly be the guilty one.

233
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:17,799
You're being overly concerned.

234
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:19,279
There's nothing

235
00:11:19,679 --> 00:11:20,919
to discuss between us.

236
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:25,919
By the way,

237
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,879
the Mid-Autumn Festival is coming up.

238
00:11:28,279 --> 00:11:29,519
My niece

239
00:11:29,759 --> 00:11:31,120
used to come here

240
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,600
around this time every year,

241
00:11:33,399 --> 00:11:35,240
claiming to visit me,

242
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,360
but really,

243
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:37,559
it was all for you.

244
00:11:38,679 --> 00:11:39,440
Your father

245
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:41,399
was quite fond of her

246
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:43,919
and considered marrying her to you.

247
00:11:45,879 --> 00:11:47,080
I'll take care of it.

248
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:50,039
Yunzhou,

249
00:11:50,559 --> 00:11:52,120
although you and Lady Yin

250
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:53,720
are about to get married,

251
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:54,279
but

252
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:58,279
my niece likes you so much.

253
00:11:58,799 --> 00:12:00,480
I think she would be willing

254
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:02,039
to be your concubine.

255
00:12:03,679 --> 00:12:04,440
How about

256
00:12:04,759 --> 00:12:05,960
you take her as your concubine

257
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:08,440
after the festival?

258
00:12:08,799 --> 00:12:09,879
It would be

259
00:12:09,879 --> 00:12:12,240
a good deed.

260
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:15,000
My fiancée is still in prison.

261
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:17,440
Even if she's released,

262
00:12:18,799 --> 00:12:20,720
she's unworthy of the Xiao Family.

263
00:12:22,039 --> 00:12:22,639
However,

264
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:25,360
engagement and annulment

265
00:12:25,799 --> 00:12:27,039
must follow proper etiquette.

266
00:12:27,519 --> 00:12:28,919
We can't rush it.

267
00:12:29,639 --> 00:12:31,120
We must consult the Patriarch

268
00:12:31,679 --> 00:12:33,320
and consult with the elders.

269
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:35,679
It must also be recorded in the ancestral hall,

270
00:12:36,399 --> 00:12:37,440
only then can it be considered done.

271
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:39,919
You,

272
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:42,600
you're always tough on the outside, soft on the inside.

273
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:45,159
You're deeply in love with her.

274
00:12:45,159 --> 00:12:47,000
How could you just decide to break off the engagement like this?

275
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,159
But the Yin family

276
00:12:50,679 --> 00:12:52,240
is now disgraced.

277
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:54,360
It's indeed not suitable for a high-born family like us.

278
00:12:54,879 --> 00:12:56,159
The Xiao Family's reputation,

279
00:12:56,159 --> 00:12:57,480
and the clan's prestige,

280
00:12:58,360 --> 00:13:00,399
I must consider them.

281
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:05,039
Though the Xiao Family isn't noble,

282
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:07,240
we're a respected family in this city.

283
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:10,000
How can we allow a tainted person

284
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:11,240
to stain our name?

285
00:13:12,679 --> 00:13:14,559
The Yin Family is already implicated.

286
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,559
The engagement must be annulled.

287
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:19,039
Liu,

288
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,440
you're always gentle and virtuous.

289
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:24,200
If she could marry you,

290
00:13:25,360 --> 00:13:27,240
it would be a blessing for our family.

291
00:13:27,759 --> 00:13:28,320
Yunzhou,

292
00:13:28,879 --> 00:13:30,600
are you really so resolute?

293
00:13:36,639 --> 00:13:37,720
Since the tea has gone cold,

294
